= Taimali = Nsgan Taimali o gaga Nsgan Taitung, kmpraan kana dxgal o 102.29 km², (dxgal dgiyaq o 4.53 km², dxgal pmblxan o 57.38 km²). kmhbragan hiyi o 7,128, sapah o 2,979, seejiq tnpusu 4,782 hiyi, knhbragan hiyi o 67% (Paywang, Sbnawan). Paywang, Sbnawan ka hbaraw balay alang hini.
